comment: Noel (PHI) makes contact with Green's (MIA) body that affects his shot attempt.
McConnell (PHI) steps OOB while in possession of the ball.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that McConnell (PHI) stepped OOB while in possession of the ball was upheld.
[Observable in enhanced video] Wade (MIA) switches his pivot foot while attempting to escape from the double team.
Wade( MIA) is granted a timeout prior to committing a backcourt violation.
Covington (PHI) commits a take foul on Green (MIA).
Covington (PHI) cleanly strips the ball from Dragic (MIA), who falls trying to gain possession.

[Observable in production angle] RHH shows Bosh (MIA) maintains a legal guarding position as he attempts to block Covington's (PHI) shot. Covington hits Bosh's leg with his foot as he passes. Unclear if Bosh's leg was extended slightly before contact or if contact pulled it (appears latter).
Covington (PHI) commits a take foul on Green (MIA).
